## Examples

The following examples show how to use this InSpec audit resource.

### Test for blocking .htaccess files on CentOS

    describe apache_conf do
      its('AllowOverride') { should eq 'None' }
    end

### Test ports for SSL

    describe apache_conf do
      its('Listen') { should eq '443'}
    end
